deps.context: find_package(ffmpeg components avformat avcodec avutil swscale swresample)

libs.content:
find_library(winmm_library names winmm
        paths 
        path_suffixes lib lib/x86 lib/x64)
find_library(coreaudio_framework names coreaudio)
find_library(audiotoolbox_library names audiotoolbox)

find_program(bin2h_native_command names bin2h
        paths "${alsoft_native_tools_path}"
        no_default_path)

find_program(bsincgen_native_command names bsincgen
        paths "${alsoft_native_tools_path}"
        no_default_path)
find_program(sed_executable names sed doc "sed executable")
find_program(dlltool_executable names "dlltool" doc "dlltool executable")
find_library(_ffmpeg_have_libz names z)

find_library(qsa_library
                 names asound
                 doc "the qsa library"
    )

find_library(sdl2_core_library
  names sdl2
  hints
  $env{sdl2dir}
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  paths
  /sw
  /opt/local
  /opt/csw
  /opt
)

find_library(sdl2main_library
      names sdl2main
      hints
      $env{sdl2dir}
      path_suffixes lib64 lib
      paths
      /sw
      /opt/local
      /opt/csw
      /opt
    )

find_library(sdl_sound_library
    names sdl_sound
    hints
        env sdlsounddir
        env sdldir
)
find_library(math_library names m)

find_library(mikmod_library
                        names libmikmod-coreaudio mikmod
                        paths
                            env mikmoddir
                            env sdlsounddir
                            env sdldir
                            /sw
                            /opt/local
                            /opt/csw
                            /opt
                        path_suffixes lib
                    )

find_library(modplug_library
                        names modplug
                        paths
                            env modplugdir
                            env sdlsounddir
                            env sdldir
                            /sw
                            /opt/local
                            /opt/csw
                            /opt
                        path_suffixes lib
                    )

find_library(vorbisfile_library
                        names vorbisfile vorbisfile vorbisfile
                        paths
                            env vorbisdir
                            env oggdir
                            env sdlsounddir
                            env sdldir
                            /sw
                            /opt/local
                            /opt/csw
                            /opt
                        path_suffixes lib
                    )

find_library(vorbis_library
                        names vorbis vorbis vorbis
                        paths
                            env oggdir
                            env vorbisdir
                            env sdlsounddir
                            env sdldir
                            /sw
                            /opt/local
                            /opt/csw
                            /opt
                        path_suffixes lib
                    )

find_library(ogg_library
                        names ogg ogg ogg
                        paths
                            env oggdir
                            env vorbisdir
                            env sdlsounddir
                            env sdldir
                            /sw
                            /opt/local
                            /opt/csw
                            /opt
                        path_suffixes lib
                    )

find_library(smpeg_library
                        names smpeg smpeg smpeg smpeg
                        paths
                            env smpegdir
                            env sdlsounddir
                            env sdldir
                            /sw
                            /opt/local
                            /opt/csw
                            /opt
                        path_suffixes lib
                    )

find_library(flac_library
                        names flac flac
                        paths
                            env flacdir
                            env sdlsounddir
                            env sdldir
                            /sw
                            /opt/local
                            /opt/csw
                            /opt
                        path_suffixes lib
                    )

find_library(speex_library
                        names speex speex
                        paths
                            env speexdir
                            env sdlsounddir
                            env sdldir
                            /sw
                            /opt/local
                            /opt/csw
                            /opt
                        path_suffixes lib
                    )

find_library(ogg_library
                            names ogg ogg ogg
                            paths
                                env oggdir
                                env vorbisdir
                                env speexdir
                                env sdlsounddir
                                env sdldir
                                /sw
                                /opt/local
                                /opt/csw
                                /opt
                            path_suffixes lib
                        )

find_library(dsound_library
             names dsound
             paths "${dxsdk_dir}" ${winsdk_lib_dirs}
             path_suffixes lib lib/x86 lib/x64
             doc "the directsound library")

find_library(pulseaudio_library
             names pulse
             doc "the pulseaudio library"
)

find_library(oss_library
             names ossaudio
             doc "optional oss library"
)

find_library(portaudio_library
             names portaudio
             doc "the portaudio library"
)

find_library(soundio_library
             names sndio
             doc "the soundio library"
)
